1
00:00:00,376 --> 00:00:04,900
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,900 --> 00:00:10,404
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,404 --> 00:00:16,832
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,832 --> 00:00:21,312
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,312 --> 00:00:25,760
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:30,671
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,671 --> 00:00:34,720
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:39,255
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,255 --> 00:00:43,552
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,552 --> 00:00:48,317
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,317 --> 00:00:51,808
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,808 --> 00:00:55,488
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,134 --> 00:01:00,512
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,512 --> 00:01:03,200
=Episode 27=

15
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:10,666
It's not my fault.

16
00:01:11,933 --> 00:01:13,633
You forced me into this.

17
00:01:15,424 --> 00:01:16,768
(Lan Rensha)

18
00:01:17,166 --> 00:01:18,666
You can't blame me.

19
00:01:24,233 --> 00:01:26,566
Indeed, we've worked very hard.

20
00:01:26,733 --> 00:01:28,366
We conducted massive market research.

21
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:30,833
Finally, we released
this successful product.

22
00:01:32,033 --> 00:01:34,733
You still look energetic at this age.

23
00:01:35,033 --> 00:01:36,733
I am really impressed.

24
00:01:38,266 --> 00:01:42,300
Mr. Zeng, I think we can collaborate.

25
00:01:42,833 --> 00:01:44,133
We should be qualified now, right?

26
00:01:45,733 --> 00:01:47,633
Your company has long been qualified.

27
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,528
However...

28
00:01:51,133 --> 00:01:52,533
What is it, Mr. Zeng?

29
00:01:52,833 --> 00:01:54,766
Your new product is fairly successful.

30
00:01:55,466 --> 00:01:56,733
But I always think

31
00:01:56,733 --> 00:01:59,500
a product
without a soul is not sustainable.

32
00:02:03,866 --> 00:02:05,433
Stop beating around the bush.

33
00:02:06,633 --> 00:02:10,166
If you don't want to cooperate,
just say it. Don't waste time.

34
00:02:12,866 --> 00:02:14,766
Please calm down. Take care.

35
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,033
Yes, grandfather, calm down.

36
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:21,300
I think Mr. Zeng must have his reasons.

37
00:02:22,033 --> 00:02:25,833
Yes, your company is still
on our final evaluation list.

38
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:28,233
Please refine your financing plan

39
00:02:29,966 --> 00:02:32,433
and bid then. Thank you.

40
00:02:33,433 --> 00:02:36,833
I've told you to marry Gu Qianqian.
With the influence of the Gu family,

41
00:02:37,466 --> 00:02:40,333
we wouldn't have been humiliated
by him.

42
00:02:50,233 --> 00:02:54,500
Alright. Everyone's worked hard.

43
00:02:55,466 --> 00:02:56,633
Let's go out for lunch.

44
00:03:00,033 --> 00:03:04,400
Miss Jin, you go eat outside
with Lan Chen.

45
00:03:06,433 --> 00:03:07,808
The two of us?

46
00:03:09,233 --> 00:03:12,700
You two should go out
and relax while eating.

47
00:03:13,633 --> 00:03:15,800
I have a meeting with Mr. Li.

48
00:03:15,866 --> 00:03:18,000
- Yes.
- You two go.

49
00:03:39,033 --> 00:03:42,500
Boss, you can talk to me
if you have any worries.

50
00:03:52,733 --> 00:03:54,033
Well...

51
00:03:59,966 --> 00:04:01,633
Can you be my girlfriend?

52
00:04:09,433 --> 00:04:12,300
We haven't known each other for long.

53
00:04:15,766 --> 00:04:17,700
Let's get to know each other better.

54
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:22,166
We haven't spent enough time together?

55
00:04:23,066 --> 00:04:24,733
I think it's enough.

56
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:28,966
I think you like Zeng...

57
00:04:35,666 --> 00:04:37,366
It's okay. Let's eat.

58
00:04:39,933 --> 00:04:41,700
I'll go to the restroom.

59
00:04:55,466 --> 00:04:57,800
Xi'en, why are you here?

60
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:01,533
I'm having lunch with Lan Chen.

61
00:05:03,433 --> 00:05:04,832
Okay.

62
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:10,533
Thank you for giving me the chance
to be confessed.

63
00:05:11,733 --> 00:05:13,133
What are you talking about?

64
00:05:16,166 --> 00:05:17,733
I rejected Lan Chen.

65
00:05:20,066 --> 00:05:20,933
Why?

66
00:05:21,066 --> 00:05:23,300
He confessed to me,

67
00:05:24,166 --> 00:05:25,800
but he actually talked to you.

68
00:05:27,866 --> 00:05:29,233
You must get him wrong.

69
00:05:30,733 --> 00:05:35,900
No, I've decided to start over
and compete fairly with you.

70
00:05:38,866 --> 00:05:42,900
By the way, I heard
your new product has been launched.

71
00:05:45,233 --> 00:05:49,433
Mr. Zeng said at the meeting today
that it's still not good enough.

72
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:54,000
What? With such good sales,

73
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,266
everyone would want to invest.

74
00:05:55,266 --> 00:05:59,700
No, Mr. Zeng said
the product lacks a soul.

75
00:06:00,566 --> 00:06:02,300
He also mentioned the financing plan.

76
00:06:05,066 --> 00:06:07,600
Impossible. Mr. Lan
and I both think the plan is good.

77
00:06:10,733 --> 00:06:14,433
If you think so,
I'll have nothing to say.

78
00:06:15,833 --> 00:06:17,433
Alright.

79
00:06:17,433 --> 00:06:21,533
There must be some misunderstanding.
I'll go ask Mr. Zeng.

80
00:06:21,833 --> 00:06:23,233
- Alright.
- Alright.

81
00:06:23,233 --> 00:06:24,704
Okay.

82
00:06:34,333 --> 00:06:35,200
What are you doing here?

83
00:06:35,968 --> 00:06:37,600
I'm afraid that you fell asleep.

84
00:06:39,466 --> 00:06:42,500
You got changed?

85
00:06:43,966 --> 00:06:46,333
Yes.

86
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,166
Is it because you got something on them?

87
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,100
Yes.

88
00:06:58,533 --> 00:06:59,900
Alright, well,

89
00:07:00,466 --> 00:07:01,433
go back and eat.

90
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,300
After lunch, I'll take you home.

91
00:07:03,866 --> 00:07:04,900
Have a good rest.

92
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,233
Okay.

93
00:07:07,233 --> 00:07:09,500
I'll do as you say.

94
00:07:26,066 --> 00:07:28,233
What do you think is the soul
of the product?

95
00:07:30,066 --> 00:07:31,566
It means the inner essence.

96
00:07:32,033 --> 00:07:34,912
How can a product last without love?

97
00:07:38,966 --> 00:07:41,500
I mean, it's the same
with clothing design.

98
00:07:41,833 --> 00:07:44,566
I think good clothing design needs love,

99
00:07:44,666 --> 00:07:46,366
and accumulation.

100
00:07:47,833 --> 00:07:49,300
Why are you talking
about clothing design?

101
00:07:49,633 --> 00:07:51,600
You are bringing up another topic.

102
00:07:53,566 --> 00:07:55,366
What do you mean by that?

103
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,133
Isn't this just a metaphor?

104
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:01,600
Besides, today's the weekend.
I'm not your employee. Speak properly.

105
00:08:06,966 --> 00:08:08,633
I suspect you have schizophrenia.

106
00:08:09,133 --> 00:08:10,100
You're always changing.

107
00:08:10,566 --> 00:08:11,633
Miss Jin.

108
00:08:14,533 --> 00:08:15,600
You are really special.

109
00:08:26,433 --> 00:08:29,000
Haven't you been eating well lately?

110
00:08:32,466 --> 00:08:35,566
We're together every day.
Don't you know about that?

111
00:08:37,266 --> 00:08:40,633
Come on. Just tell me directly.

112
00:08:40,633 --> 00:08:43,733
Alright, enough.

113
00:08:46,233 --> 00:08:47,399
I mean...

114
00:08:48,633 --> 00:08:50,299
You need to take good care of yourself.

115
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:52,033
Anyway, don't push yourself so hard.

116
00:09:04,431 --> 00:09:08,953
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

117
00:09:11,983 --> 00:09:16,944
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

118
00:09:19,993 --> 00:09:25,817
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

119
00:09:25,817 --> 00:09:33,287
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

120
00:09:33,287 --> 00:09:36,768
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

121
00:09:36,768 --> 00:09:40,889
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

122
00:09:40,889 --> 00:09:42,585
♪Open my secret♪

123
00:09:42,585 --> 00:09:48,633
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

124
00:09:48,633 --> 00:09:52,505
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

125
00:09:52,505 --> 00:09:57,011
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

126
00:09:57,011 --> 00:10:05,721
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
